013package org.apache.juneau.xml.annotation;
014
015import static java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy.*;
016
017import java.lang.annotation.*;
018
019/**
020 * Namespace name/URL mapping pair.
021 *
022 * <p>
023 * Used to identify a namespace/URI pair on a {@link XmlSchema#xmlNs() @XmlSchema(xmlNs)} annotation.
024 *
025 * <ul class='seealso'>
026 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="../../../../../overview-summary.html#juneau-marshall.jm.XmlDetails">XML Details</a>
027
028 * </ul>
029 */
030@Documented
031@Target({})
032@Retention(RUNTIME)
033@Inherited
034public @interface XmlNs {
035
036   /**
037    * XML namespace URL.
038    *
039    * @return The annotation value.
040    */
041   String namespaceURI();
042
043   /**
044    * XML namespace prefix.
045    *
046    * @return The annotation value.
047    */
048   String prefix();
049}
